title: Cup and Saucer Cafe - North
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Long-standing Portland breakfast and lunch cafe with multiple locations. Has marked vegan items, such as pancakes, scrambles, biscuits and gravy;offers tofu, vegan cheese, garden sausage, vegan pestos and other sides; non-dairy milks for add-ons and subsitutions.
